image_analysis.description: A high-resolution photograph of a luxury bedroom. The room features a large bed with a dark wood headboard and white linens, positioned against a wall with blue and white floral wallpaper. A distinctive, large blue glass chandelier hangs from the ceiling. In front of the bed is a curved, cream-colored upholstered bench or sofa. The floor is covered with a white carpet featuring a bold blue grid pattern. Two dark wood nightstands with matching lamps flank the bed. To the left, a tall, dark wood door with decorative panels is partially visible.
image_analysis.layout: Interior room shot, centered on the bed and chandelier.
